 dead, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Or those who are dead"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that, although they might be judged in the flesh according to human standards, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:18","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" they might live "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:21","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the spirit according to God’s standards."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 5:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"1Pt 3:18","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"Php 1:21","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":5,"text":"Or those who are dead"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:4:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The end of all things is near; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 13:11–12","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:26","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 5:8","book":"Jas","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:3","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" therefore, be alert and sober-minded "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" for prayer. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 13:11–12","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 9:26","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"Jms 5:8","book":"Jas","chapter":5,"verse":8},{"label":"1Jn 2:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":18},{"label":"Rv 1:3","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Pt 5:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:4:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Above all, maintain c