d may be glorified through Jesus Christ in everything. To him be the glory and the power forever and ever. Amen."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:6–8","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":6},{"label":"1Co 15:58","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":58}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:4:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Dear friends, don’t be surprised when the fiery ordeal comes among you to test you, as if something unusual were happening to you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 1:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:4:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Instead, rejoice as you share in the sufferings of Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:24","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:10","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that you may also rejoice with great joy when his glory is revealed. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:7","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:17","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 5:24","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":24},{"label":"Php 3:10","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"1Co 1:7","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Eph 1:17","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"1Pt 1:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"1Pt 1:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe: